{"tid":2030372,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2016年8月5日 香港史上第一次亦應該係最後一次以港獨為主題既集會","createTime":"2020-05-22T16:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T17:13:07.000Z","uid":41411,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aab0783eb60d3ccc8d4637e8e34550d00c80ee0c","tid":2030372,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"梁天琦，陳浩天 2個當時香港人 由其年輕人既新希望 <br />\n可惜都比港共政權打壓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBN4JOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBN4JOV.jpg&h=71dcc846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時社會仲對港獨議題好避忌同敏感<br />\n竟然有接近一萬個人出席集會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvtrW9H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvtrW9H.png&h=b719b75b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家國安法殺到黎 唔好講以港獨為題既集會<br />\n你講左依2隻字 出個po有港獨2隻字都即刻拉你<br />\n依一日 香港人要永遠記住 納入史冊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港獨立，唯一出路</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c9844aa81cd9e567281df2c4bce551a0e0b1a236","tid":2030372,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:48:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e74e19a90d5a8d8259646188a4af3cbafecf65","tid":2030372,"uid":245711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:52:42.000Z","msg":"天琦無稿演講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d285ca50edba6438c11ddd6812cbe0d19589c5","tid":2030372,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03e74e19a90d5a8d8259646188a4af3cbafecf65","tid":2030372,"uid":245711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:52:42.000Z","msg":"天琦無稿演講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"極高汁"}]}